cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper presents a method for analyzing white matter tracts using diffusion measures and geometrical properties, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI). The application of the method to contact sports players suggests a focus on medical imaging (cs.SI).
